text: Code page 3846 is a modification of code page 437 to support the Turkish language. This code page is supported by Star printersStar LC 8021 User's Manual and FreeDOS. == Character set == The following tables show code page 3846. Each character is shown with its equivalent Unicode code point and its decimal Alt code.
